de.schenk.jrtrace.annotations

Annotation Type XParam


  • @Retention(value=CLASS)
@Target(value=PARAMETER)
public @interface XParam
    If a parameter of the injected method is annotated with XParam the value of one of the arguments of the target method will be injected into this parameter when called. It is in the responsibility of the developer to ensure that the types of the target method parameter and the injected method parameter match.
    Author:
    Christian Schenk
